Task: Individually controlling each digit of the segment with the joystick
a. Using the X-axis, cycle through the digits and chose which one to modify. Light up the
DP led of the current position
b. Press the button to lock on the selected digit
c. After that, use the Y-axis to modify the value of the digit, both up and down.
d. Press the button again to unlock the selection and be able to cycle through the 4 digits
again
e. (WITH BONUS)There are 3 states: locked in / selected (not locked in though) / not selected. They are all diferentiated 
with 
    1) blinking digit+point as selected(not locked)
    2)point as lockedIN
    3)just conitnuous digit for the others


One delay usage for the delay between different digits shown. 
